rows.label: tlk41200126_01_msg0001
rows.name: Do you know what a Torigonda is?

rows.label: tlk41200126_01_msg0002
rows.name: It's the instrument I'm playing right now.

rows.label: tlk41200126_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I practice with all my might every night,
but I'm still not there yet.

rows.label: tlk41200126_01_msg0004
rows.name:
All Gulans love music, you see.
If you don't get really good, you won't
be acknowledged.
